@NODE "Installation" "Installation"
@TOC "Main"

@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
                           I N S T A L L A T I O N
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
   If you just what to try out T2S there is no need for you to install the 
main executable, but you will need to copy the music to the S: directory on 
either your Workbench disk or your Hard drive, like this:

        · @{" Open a CLI " SYSTEM "NewCli"}
        · Type in: `Copy WB-FunPak:S/Backbeat S:'
        · Close the CLI by typing `EndCli'
        · Double Click on the T2S Icon!

   If you like T2S then just copy the T2S file to your WBStartup drawer 
on your WB disk or Hard drive!
 
   @{" Back to the Contents Page! " LINK "Main"}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "Usage" "Usage"
@TOC "Main"

@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
                                  U S A G E
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
   To use T2S just double click on its icon providing you have @{" Installed " LINK "Installation"}
any relevant files like the music first! T2S will open its own window at 
the bottom of the Workbench screen, you won`t be able to quit or stop the 
music; you have been warned.

   @{" Back to the Contents Page! " LINK "Main"}
@ENDNODE

@NODE "KnownBugs" "Erros/Bugs"
@TOC "Main"

@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
                            E R R O R S / B U G S
@{FG SHINE}____________________________________________________________________________@{FG TEXT}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
   One error I have incountered while using T2S is when the program does 
not find the music and opens a window saying `Illegal Sound File'. This 
basicly means it can`t find the music, if this happens make sure you 
have @{" Installed " LINK "Installation"} the music to the S: directory.

   Also, I find that after a while the program seems to crash out, but the 
music still plays, I am in the process of finding out what causes the bug 
and will re-release this program when, and only when it is fixed.

   You may also notice some lottery numbers may come out more than once, 
I`ll try to fix this bug by the next version!

   @{" Back to the Contents Page! " LINK "Main"}
